<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta http-equiv="content-type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">
    <title>Annotare 2.0 is unavailable</title>
    <style type="text/css">
        ::-webkit-scrollbar {
            width: 7px;
            height: 7px;
        }

        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
            width: 7px;
            height: 7px;
            -webkit-border-radius:3px;
            border-radius:3px;
            background:rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }

        html, body {
            font-family: 'Arial Unicode MS', Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bolder;
            padding-bottom: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            margin-top: 5px;
            color: #207A7A;
        }

        a, a:link, a:visited {
            color: #185C5C;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .copy {
            padding-top: 3px;
            font-size: small;
            color: #207A7A;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .outer {
            position: absolute;
            top: 30%;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .inner {
            width: 500px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .frame {
            padding: 15px 10px 2px;
            font-size: small;
        }

        .error {
            font-size: small;
            color: red;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .info {
            font-size: small;
            color: darkgreen;
            text-align: left;
        }

        table {
            border-collapse: collapse;
            color: #000;
            width: 100%;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .form td {
            padding: 0 3px;
        }

        .form tr td:first-child {
            white-space: nowrap;
        }

        .form tr.row td {
            padding-top: 5px;
            padding-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .form tr.right td {
            text-align: right;
        }

        .form input {
            padding: 5px 4px;
            border: 1px solid #CCC;
            border-top: 1px solid #999;
            font-size: small;
            font-family: Arial Unicode MS, Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        .form button {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 5px 7px;
            text-decoration: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            cursor: hand;
            font-size: small;
            border: 1px solid #BBB;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #A0A0A0;
            border-radius: 3px;
            -moz-border-radius: 3px;
            background: white;
        }

        .at-bottom {
            width:100%;
            position:absolute;
            bottom:0;
            left:0;
            text-align:center;
        }
        </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="outer">
    <div class="inner">
        <div class="frame">
            <div>Dear submitters. Unfortunately, technical problems prevent Annotare from functionning at the moment.
                Our engineers are working to restore the service as soon as possible. Should you have an urgent matter,
                please contact us at <a href="mailto:annotare@ebi.ac.uk">annotare@ebi.ac.uk</a>. Apologies for the inconvenience.</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="at-bottom copy">2014 EMBL-EBI, Functional Genomics Group</div>
</body>
</html>


